      "text": "started normally. Approximately 3 hours later in the same",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "swamp area, but away from the road where the work crew was",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "cutting \"hay\", he surreptitiously, because of the German",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
